# Component Design Patterns

## Atomic Design Hierarchy

```
Atoms → Molecules → Organisms → Templates → Pages

Atoms: Button, Input, Icon
Molecules: SearchBar (Input + Button)
Organisms: Header (Logo + Nav + SearchBar)
Templates: Page layout structure
Pages: Final implementation
```

## Component Anatomy

```tsx
<Component>
  <ComponentHeader>
    {/* Icon/Avatar */}
    {/* Title */}
    {/* Actions */}
  </ComponentHeader>

  <ComponentBody>
    {/* Main content */}
  </ComponentBody>

  <ComponentFooter>
    {/* Secondary actions */}
  </ComponentFooter>
</Component>
```

## Design Specifications Example

```markdown
## Card Component

### Props:
- variant: 'elevated' | 'outlined' | 'filled'
- size: 'sm' | 'md' | 'lg'
- hoverable: boolean
- clickable: boolean

### Visual:
- Padding: 16px (md)
- Border radius: 12px
- Shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1)
- Border: 1px solid #e0e0e0 (outlined)
```

## Responsive Patterns

```typescript
